ISLAMABAD, Mar 13 (APP): Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib said on Sunday that today, Prime Minister Imran Khan will address a historic public meeting in Hafizabad district.
In a tweet, from village to village, town to town, every neighborhood of Hafizabad, people were flocking to the stadium to receive their selfless and courageous leader.
